Add an `is_initialized` flag to state and check it at the start of `initialize`, or use Anchor's `#[account(init)]` which ensures the account was just created (lamports == 0) and sets the discriminator.
```rust
require!(!state.is_initialized, ErrorCode::AlreadyInitialized);
state.is_initialized = true;
```

